This project is dual-licensed (open-core).

The gateway/server is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License,
version 3 only (AGPL-3.0-only). The client and the shared core are licensed
under the Apache License, version 2.0 (Apache-2.0). This split keeps the client
distributable on the Mac App Store, which cannot carry AGPL software, while the
AGPL keeps the hosted gateway open.

Directory -> licence map:

  AGPL-3.0-only:
    cmd/gateway/
    internal/gateway/
    gateway-only deploy assets under deploy/ that contain gateway server logic

  Apache-2.0 (everything the client ships or links, plus shared tooling):
    apps/macos/
    pkg/clientcore/
    pkg/protocoltypes/
    pkg/testkit/
    internal/protocol/
    internal/dedup/
    internal/transport/
    internal/paths/
    internal/platform/
    internal/diagnostics/
    internal/bootstrap/
    cmd/continuityctl/
    and the rest of the shared core and tooling

